name: Radiotracker Wishlist File
summary: Learn about .RTWSH files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: Music wishlists can be saved and opened from the Music wishes tab in the Audials Radiotracker software.
NOTE: Wishlists are more commonly saved using the .A1WISH extension.

description: Music wishlist created by Audials Radiotracker, a program used for recording online radio station streams; contains a list of artists and songs that the user would like to find playing on an Internet radio station; uses a simple XML format.
